	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Balto.</placeName> <date>June 4th 1857</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I had this pleasure yester&#45;<lb/>day in registered letter&#44; with enclosure &#36;109.96&#47;100&#44;<lb/> in full of accot.  Referring to my remarks<lb/> in same I give below a copy of the statement<lb/> handed me by <persName>Dr. Guinsburg</persName></p>
				<table rows="17" cols="3">
				<row>
				<cell><persName>Mr Is. Leeser</persName></cell>
				<cell/>
				<cell>Cr</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>For 2 doz. Readers &#64;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;4.&#95;&#95;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;8.00</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#8220; 2 &#8220; <persName>Nath</persName> &#8220; &#8220;</cell>
				<cell>2.40</cell>
				<cell>4.80</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#8220; 2 &#8220; <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest. &#8220;</cell>
				<cell>4.80</cell>
				<cell>9.60</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#8220; 1 &#8220; Catechisms &#8220;</cell>
				<cell/>
				<cell>6.&#8212;</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#8220; 1 &#8220; Prayer Book</cell>
				<cell/>
				 <cell><hi rend="underline"> 2.&#8212;</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;30.40</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>Dr</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell><persName>Mr Cohen</persName>&#44; for him returned</cell>
				<cell/>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>18 Readers</cell>
				<cell>&#36;6.&#8212;</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>18 <persName>Nath.</persName> Readers</cell>
				<cell>3.60</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>19 <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest.</cell>
				<cell>7.60</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>11 Catechisms</cell>
				<cell>5.50</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>1 Prayer Book</cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">2.&#8212;</hi></cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;24.70</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>To Commo.10&#37;</cell>
				<cell>&#8212;.57</cell>
				<cell>25.27</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>Sold</cell>
				<cell>5.13&#47;100</cell>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>I find some difference between his statement<lb/> as handed me&#44; &#38; the number of books handed me.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<table rows="6" cols="3">
				<row>
				<cell role="label"></cell>
				<cell role="label"><persName>Dr. G&#39;s</persName> a&#47;c calls for</cell>
				<cell role="label">The numbers handed me</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>Readers</cell>
				<cell>18</cell>
				<cell>18</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell><persName>Nath.</persName> Readers</cell>
				<cell>18</cell>
				<cell>19</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell><persName>Pix.</persName> Questions</cell>
				<cell>19</cell>
				<cell>17</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>Catechisms</cell>
				<cell>11</cell>
				<cell>11</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>Prayer Book</cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">1</hi></cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">1</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>67 Books</cell>
				<cell>66 Books</cell>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>The differences amounts to but little&#44; but I will<lb/> see him and have it put right.  I have the<lb/> Books in my possession &#38; will do with them<lb/> as you may direct.  Expecting to hear from<lb/> you soon I remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Very Resptfy</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">Edward Cohen</persName></p>
